descriptionHtml:
FNIS NEW DANCE ANIMATIONS COMPILATION 

REQUIREMENTS:
 - download FNIS Idle spells v2 or higher > http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/11811

HOW TO USE:
 - just follow \"how to use\" on the FNIS idle spells v2 link or read me (i think)

Installation:
 - extract files manually to the \"DATA\" folder in ur skyrim directory
 - or use NMM (nexus mod manager)

Description
 - this is a compilation of dance animations
 - This dance animations are made by other users and is not my property
 - i dont really know how to contact the real authors (there\'s so many of them)
